sources.description:
WHAT GOOD IS A GUN AGAINST A SHADOW?! 
Occupants of a London boarding house become suspects as a string of murders are discovered.

Director: D. Ross Lederman
Writers: Anthony Coldeway, Frank Vosper 
Stars: Frieda Inescort, Paul Cavanagh, Heather Angel 
Genres: Crime, Drama, Film-Noir, Mystery, Romance, Thriller
